citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process between 12:15pm-
12:45pm on 17-JAN-24.
The inspector arrived at the facility at 12:15pm and attempted to contact the facility by knocking on the door multiple
times. The inspector also left voicemails on both account phone numbers as well as sent text messages to these
numbers. The inspector left after 30 minutes of no contact from the facility.
End Section

narrative:
2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process between 12:15pm-
12:45pm on 17-JAN-24.  
 
The inspector arrived at the facility at 12:15pm and attempted to contact the facility by knocking on the door multiple 
times. The inspector also left voicemails on both account phone numbers as well as sent text messages to these 
numbers. The inspector left after 30 minutes of no contact from the facility. 
 
 
End Section
